    "ArticleTitle": "Applications of diagnostic ultrasound and radionuclides to cardiovascular diagnosis. Part I. Acquired cardiovascular disease in the adult.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "353",
      "EndPage": "386",
      "MedlinePgn": "353-86"
